  "title": "Administrative Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are looking for a committed, diligent and dedicated staff to join our SCC @ AMK team to perform the following duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct pre-admission assessments, answering client or NOK (Next-Of-Kin) questions</li><li>Prepare and maintain new client’s personal file</li><li>Assist to plan activities with the Care Staffs and encourage seniors to participate in activity</li><li>Assist to conduct and participate activities with the seniors</li><li>Conduct house visits for vulnerable clients</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li><li>Fluent in Mandarin - Clients are majority mandarin/dialect speaking </li><li>Minimum Diploma qualification</li></ul>",
